---
import ContentLayout from "../layouts/ContentLayout.astro";
---

<ContentLayout
    title="ROX: Ruling Our eXperiences"
    description="An evidence-based empowerment program for girls in grades 7-12 at Green Local Schools."
    showBreadcrumbs={true}
    breadcrumbs={[
        { name: "Foundation Initiatives", href: "/foundation-initiatives" },
        { name: "ROX Program", href: "/rox" }
    ]}
>
    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Empowering Girls to Lead</h2>
        <p>
            ROX (Ruling Our eXperiences) is an evidence-based program that trains and licenses counselors and educators to deliver a 20-week empowering curriculum for girls. This program does extensive research on the complex issues impacting today's girls and focuses on creating stronger girls, safer schools, and successful students.
        </p>
        <p>
            The Green Schools Foundation is proud to support this important program, which is offered to girls in 7th through 12th grade at Green Local Schools.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-2 mb-12">
        <div>
            <img
                src="/images/rox/rox-girls-1.webp"
                alt="ROX program participants"
                class="rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full"
            />
        </div>
        <div>
            <img
                src="/images/rox/rox-girls-2.webp"
                alt="ROX program students"
                class="rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full"
            />
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="highlight-box">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-4">Program Goals</h2>
        <div class="grid-2">
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Building Stronger Girls</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Develop confidence and self-esteem</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Build leadership skills</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Learn to navigate complex social situations</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Make positive life choices</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Creating Safer Schools</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Reduce bullying and relational aggression</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Foster healthy peer relationships</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Create supportive environments</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span>Address issues before they escalate</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>About the Program</h2>
        <div class="grid-2">
            <div>
                <h3>Evidence-Based Curriculum</h3>
                <p>
                    The ROX program is built on extensive research into the complex issues impacting today's girls. Topics covered include self-esteem, healthy relationships, online safety, decision-making, and more. The curriculum is delivered by trained and licensed facilitators who create a safe, supportive environment for girls to learn and grow.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Program Details</h3>
                <div class="space-y-3 mt-4">
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6 2a1 1 0 00-1 1v1H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2h-1V3a1 1 0 10-2 0v1H7V3a1 1 0 00-1-1zm0 5a1 1 0 000 2h8a1 1 0 100-2H6z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Duration:</strong> 20 weeks</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 9a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6zm-7 9a7 7 0 1114 0H3z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Eligible:</strong> Girls in grades 7-12</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M10.394 2.08a1 1 0 00-.788 0l-7 3a1 1 0 000 1.84L5.25 8.051a.999.999 0 01.356-.257l4-1.714a1 1 0 11.788 1.838L7.667 9.088l1.94.831a1 1 0 00.787 0l7-3a1 1 0 000-1.838l-7-3zM3.31 9.397L5 10.12v4.102a8.969 8.969 0 00-1.05-.174 1 1 0 01-.89-.89 11.115 11.115 0 01.25-3.762z"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Location:</strong> Green Local Schools</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <img
            src="/images/rox/rox-alumni.webp"
            alt="ROX program alumni group photo"
            class="rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full mb-8"
        />
    </div>

    <div class="highlight-box">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-4">Supporting Successful Students</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
            Research shows that girls who participate in ROX demonstrate improved academic performance, better attendance, and increased engagement in school activities. The program equips young women with the skills they need to succeed not just in school, but in all areas of life.
        </p>
        <div class="grid-3">
            <div class="text-center">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 text-sm">Confidence</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3.172 5.172a4 4 0 015.656 0L10 6.343l1.172-1.171a4 4 0 115.656 5.656L10 17.657l-6.828-6.829a4 4 0 010-5.656z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 text-sm">Resilience</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-secondary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path d="M13 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM18 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM14 15a4 4 0 00-8 0v3h8v-3zM6 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM16 18v-3a5.972 5.972 0 00-.75-2.906A3.005 3.005 0 0119 15v3h-3zM4.75 12.094A5.973 5.973 0 004 15v3H1v-3a3 3 0 013.75-2.906z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 text-sm">Leadership</h3>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section text-center">
        <h2>Learn More About ROX</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
            Interested in learning more about the ROX program at Green Local Schools? Contact the Green Schools Foundation for information about enrollment and program schedules.
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:greenschoolsfoundation@gmail.com?subject=ROX Program Inquiry" class="button-primary mr-4">
            Contact Us
        </a>
        <a href="/foundation-initiatives" class="button-secondary">
            See All Initiatives
        </a>
    </div>
</ContentLayout>
